OL,3,CCardiff Parkway station project
OL,4,Capproved by Welsh Government
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has given
OL,7,Fapproval of the Cardiff Parkway train
OL,8,Fstation, eight years since the idea
OL,9,Fwas initially proposed.
OL,11,FWhat is Cardiff Parkway?
OL,13,FThe Cardiff Parkway train station is
OL,14,Fpart of a proposed development in St
OL,15,FMellons, located between Cardiff and
OL,16,FNewport.
OL,18,FIt's been described as a "game
OL,19,Fchanger" by its supporters to help
OL,20,Ffill the lack of transport options in
OL,21,Fthe eastern Cardiff area.
