OL,3,CCardiff Parkway station project
OL,4,Capproved by Welsh Government
OL,6,FJourney times between Cardiff and
OL,7,FNewport could be reduced to just seven
OL,8,Fminutes, potentially benefiting more
OL,9,Fthan 800,000 passengers every year.
OL,11,FThe station will also offer
OL,12,Fsignificant Park & Ride capacity,
OL,13,Fwhich is not widely available in
OL,14,FCardiff.
OL,16,FThe project has faced significant
OL,17,Fscrutiny and delays, with the Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment ultimately granting
OL,19,Fplanning permission today following
OL,20,Finitial approval from Cardiff Council
OL,21,Fin 2022.
