OL,3,CCardiff Parkway station project
OL,4,Capproved by Welsh Government
OL,6,FWill it be good financially for the
OL,7,Farea?
OL,9,FThe project is expected to bring
OL,10,Feconomic benefits to the Cardiff
OL,11,FCapital Region with potential to bring
OL,12,Fan estimated 6,000 new jobs to the
OL,13,Farea.
OL,15,FIt's also expected to provide an
OL,16,Fannual boost of up to #265 million to
OL,17,Fthe region and #5 billion over 20
OL,18,Fyears.
