OL,3,CCardiff Parkway station project
OL,4,Capproved by Welsh Government
OL,6,FThe station is part of a wider
OL,7,Finvestment zone, designed to offer tax
OL,8,Fincentives and other perks to get
OL,9,Fbusinesses and investors on board.
OL,11,FWhy so many delays?
OL,13,FThe project has faced a long planning
OL,14,Fprocess including concerns over
OL,15,Fenvironmental impact.
OL,17,FTodays approval from The Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment's came after two public
OL,19,Fhearings and a recommendation from a
OL,20,Fplanning inspector.
