OL,3,CCardiff Parkway station project
OL,4,Capproved by Welsh Government
OL,6,FThe First Minister acknowledged that
OL,7,Frefusing planning permission would
OL,8,Fnegatively impact the government's
OL,9,Fgoals for a greener economy.
OL,11,FDevelopers have stated they are
OL,12,Fmitigating environmental impact by
OL,13,F"protecting" and "enhancing" the reens
OL,14,Fthat run through the site.
OL,16,FWhat's the reaction?
OL,18,FCardiff Council Leader, Cllr Huw
OL,19,FThomas said he was "delighted with the
OL,20,Fnews."
