OL,3,CCardiff Parkway station project
OL,4,Capproved by Welsh Government
OL,6,F"This development is not just about a
OL,7,Fnew railway station; it's about
OL,8,Fenhancing our city's future. Cardiff
OL,9,FParkway will significantly improve our
OL,10,Ftransport infrastructure, leading to
OL,11,Feconomic growth and job creation
OL,12,Facross Cardiff and the wider region
OL,14,FAndrew RT Davies MS, Senedd Member for
OL,15,FSouth Wales Central said it was
OL,16,F'better late than never,'
OL,18,F"This new station will be a game
OL,19,Fchanger for Cardiff, but we do have to
OL,20,Fask what took Welsh Government so long
OL,21,Fto approve it."
